item.title: What to eat for lunch
item.description: Translated by deepl This fact means a lot to me, and I believe it means something to the world as well. We have to face a very awkward fact, that is, Da Vinci said in an offhand way that boldness and firm determination can be worth the fineness of weapons. I hope that you will also appreciate this statement. To sum up, personally, what I eat for lunch means a lot to me.
